Manu Ramesan is an Malayalee film composer who is best known as the son of one of the most famous poets and lyricists in Kerala, S. Ramesan Nair. He has composed for films such as Pidichirukku (2008), Gulumal: The Escape (2009) and Plus Two (2010).[1] Ramesan has written lyrics for more than 450 songs for the Malayalam film industry, from 1985 onwards. 
